prediction.sparql:
PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT ?type ( COUNT( ?pub ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?pub rdf:type ?type .
  FILTER ( ?type IN ( dblp:Publication , dblp:Inproceedings , dblp:Article , dblp:Book ) )
}
GROUP BY ?type
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )

PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?name ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?pub ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?pub dblp:publishedInStream <https://dblp.org/streams/journals/sigir> ; dblp:authoredBy ?creator .
  ?creator rdfs:label ?name .
  FILTER ( REGEX( LCASE( ?name ) , "^m.*d" ) )
}
GROUP BY ?name
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )

PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
SELECT ?subtype ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?pub ) AS ?count ) ( ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?pub ) * 100.0 / 7872109 ) AS ?percentage ) WHERE {
  ?pub dblp:publishedInStream ?stream .
  BIND( IF( STRSTARTS( STR( ?stream ) , "https://dblp.org/streams/conferences/" ) , "Conference" , IF( STRSTARTS( STR( ?stream ) , "https://dblp.org/streams/journals/" ) , IF( STRSTARTS( STR( ?stream ) , "https://dblp.org/streams/journals/corr" ) , "Repository" , "Journal" ) , IF( STRSTARTS( STR( ?stream ) , "https://dblp.org/streams/series/" ) , "Series" , "Other" ) ) ) AS ?subtype )
}
GROUP BY ?subtype
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?pub ) >= 100 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
SELECT ?type ( COUNT( ?creator ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?pub dblp:authoredBy ?creator .
  ?creator rdf:type ?type
}
GROUP BY ?type
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
SELECT ?label ( COUNT( ?author ) AS ?totalAuthors ) ( COUNT( ?orcid ) AS ?orcidAuthors ) ( ( COUNT( ?orcid ) * 100.0 ) / COUNT( ?author ) AS ?percentage ) WHERE {
  ?pub dblp:publishedInStream <https://dblp.org/streams/conf/stoc> ; rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( STRENDS( ?label , ")" ) ) .
  BIND( SUBSTR( ?label , STRLEN( ?label ) - 4 , 4 ) AS ?yearStr ) .
  FILTER ( ?yearStr = "2018" ) .
  ?pub dblp:authoredBy ?author .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?author dblp:orcid ?orcid
  }
}
GROUP BY ?label
ORDER BY ?label

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?pub ?title ?authorName ?year WHERE {
  ?pub a dblp:Publication ; dblp:title ?title ; dblp:yearOfPublication ?year ; dblp:authoredBy ?creator .
  ?creator rdfs:label ?authorName .
  FILTER ( ?year <= "1940" ^^ xsd:gYear )
}
ORDER BY ?year ?title

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
SELECT ?type ( COUNT( ?entity ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?entity rdf:type ?type .
  FILTER ( ?type IN ( dblp:Publication , dblp:Creator , dblp:Stream ) )
}
GROUP BY ?type
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
